### Get all users
GET http://localhost:3003/users

### Get user by ID
GET http://localhost:3003/users/1

### Get user by ID (not found)
GET http://localhost:3003/users/999

### Get all orders
GET http://localhost:3003/orders

### Create order (valid)
POST http://localhost:3003/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "user_id": 1,
    "items": ["Laptop", "Mouse", "Keyboard"]
}

### Create order (invalid - too many items, max=5)
POST http://localhost:3003/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "user_id": 1,
    "items": ["Item1", "Item2", "Item3", "Item4", "Item5", "Item6"]
}

### Create order (invalid - user not found)
POST http://localhost:3003/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "user_id": 999,
    "items": ["Laptop"]
}

### Create order (invalid - no items)
POST http://localhost:3003/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "user_id": 1,
    "items": []
}

### Get order by ID
GET http://localhost:3003/orders/1
